Athi River of Kenya to Build Factory in South Africa, Business Daily Says

-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 
2011-08-23T03:51:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-23/athi-river-of-kenya-to-build-factory-in-south-africa-business-daily-says.html
Athi River Mining Ltd. (ARML)  plans to
build a cement factory in  South Africa  to boost its revenue by a
fifth, Business Daily reported, citing Managing Director 
Pradeep Paunrana.  The company, which is currently constructing another
factory in Tanzania, has acquired limestone minefields in South
Africa and construction of the plant is expected to  start in
two years, the Nairobi-based newspaper said.  Athi River is Kenyaâ€™s second-biggest cement maker by market
